      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;build-this-blog&#34;&gt;Build this Blog&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Medium. Hashnode. Wordpress. Ghost. Log Rocket.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There are a thousand blogging platforms that want your content, knowledge, and time. I say nay! In this article I&amp;rsquo;ll lay out all the steps you need to build this exact website and host your
content on
GitHub pages.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What you&amp;rsquo;ll get:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;input checked=&#34;&#34; disabled=&#34;&#34; type=&#34;checkbox&#34;&gt; A blogging website hosted on GitHub&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;input checked=&#34;&#34; disabled=&#34;&#34; type=&#34;checkbox&#34;&gt; The Hugo PaperMod theme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;input checked=&#34;&#34; disabled=&#34;&#34; type=&#34;checkbox&#34;&gt; Menus to filter content by categories and tags&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;input checked=&#34;&#34; disabled=&#34;&#34; type=&#34;checkbox&#34;&gt; Full text search&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;input disabled=&#34;&#34; type=&#34;checkbox&#34;&gt; Tracking with Google Analytics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2MsN8gpT6jY&#34;&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;What is Github Pages?&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;https://img.youtube.com/vi/2MsN8gpT6jY/0.jpg#center&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
